description: Cooper finds out that Ricky is cheating on his girlfriend and demands that he worship his socks and feet in exchange for silence. Cooper knows exactly how he wants Ricky to do the worshiping. First he makes Ricky sniff his white socks and then worship them on his knees. Then Cooper tells Ricky to suck his toes and clean his bare feet with his tongue. I don’t know how long Cooper will keep quiet after this. He might hold this over Ricky for a long time!
title: Cooper Demands Foot Worship
